        <div class="block text-block">
         <h3 class="block-header">
          Be Smart
          <span>
           About Safety
          </span>
         </h3>
         <div class="inner">
          <p>
           The Be Smart About Safety program is a proactive funding project that is focused on reducing potential loss in the areas of workers’ compensation, general liability, employment, auto, and property.
          </p>
          <p>
           <a href="https://risk.ucsc.edu/be-smart-about-safety.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank" title="BSAS Application">
            <img alt="BSAS Application Button" class="" height="94" src="images/button-bsas-2.png" width="323"/>
           </a>
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
